snippet.title: Conversations with Legends - DeeBoss
snippet.description:
A Nifty Island OG and a true pioneer in the metaverse. @JoeEvil and @oliver talked to @deeboss about her experience in Nifty Island, building towers and winning competitions by diving into 3D modeling.

Nifty Island wants to highlight pioneers within the community. These people are known as legends. Here is a conversation with one.

Deboss' Twitter: https://twitter.com/Dee___Boss

Nifty Island Links
Website: https://www.niftyisland.com/
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/nifty_island
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Nifty_Island 
Discord: http://discord.gg/NiftyIsland
